    "name": "Finance Analyst (Contractor)",
    "description": {
        "company": "<meta><h1 style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-size:18pt;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:24px;margin-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;\"><b><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">About Smartwyre</strong></b></h1><p style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:9pt;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.25px;margin:4px 0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:10pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Founded in 2018, Smartwyre is a venture-financed SaaS business delivering enterprise software to large agricultural businesses, operating in a $400 billion global industry. With an estimated 5 million farmers and over 5,000 distributors globally, Smartwyre works across the agricultural supply chain, from large corporations to local farms. Presently, we work from the United States, United Kingdom, Europe, and South America. </span></p><p style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10pt;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.25px;margin:4px 0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10pt;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.25px;margin:4px 0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:10pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We are building a B2B SaaS platform to network together the commercial operations of the companies that supply the world\u2019s farmers with seeds, fertilizer, chemicals, and services, with their target markets being the United States, Europe, and Latin&nbsp;America. We&nbsp;aim to first offer SaaS applications to solve key commercial pain points (pricing, costing, quoting), then network these companies using a common data platform (transactional data exchange, product information publication, people networking, and user analytics), and finally empower the network to facilitate new business model amongst network participants.</span></p>",
        "role": "<meta><h1 style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-size:18pt;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:24px;margin-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;\"><b><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">About the role</strong></b></h1><p style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.25px;margin:4px 0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Smartwyre, a rapidly expanding SaaS organization, is seeking a Finance Analyst with advanced analytical capabilities and meticulous attention to detail. The ideal candidate will</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">demonstrate</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">the ability to uphold</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">high standards</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">while actively</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">identifying</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">areas for improvement. Prior experience in a dynamic SaaS environment, robust</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">proficiency</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">in Excel, and involvement in process optimization, financial reporting, modelling, and scenario analysis are essential.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.25px;margin:4px 0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.25px;margin:4px 0px;padding:0px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">This is a contractor role and w</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:10.5pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">e are looking for an analyst for a minimum of 6 hours per day, or 30 hours per week.</span></p><p style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.25px;margin:4px 0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h1 style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-size:18pt;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:24px;margin-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;\"><b><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">What you'll do</strong></b></h1><ul data-pattern=\"discCircleSquare\" data-depth=\"1\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;margin:8px 0px;line-height:1.6;padding:0px 0px 0px 32px;list-style-type:disc;\"><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Developing budgets and providing regular forecasts with comprehensive variance analysis&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Effectively navigating complex financial spreadsheets&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Preparing companywide reports and key metrics on a routine basis&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Analyzing plan variances to deliver insights that inform action plans and strategic decisions&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Assessing cost and revenue data to</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">identify</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">opportunities, risks, and trends affecting business performance&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Producing monthly management packs, investor reports, and Board presentations&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Creating both short-term and long-term financial forecasts&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Supporting the team with ad hoc analyses and customized reporting&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Enhancing the reporting framework to drive continuous improvement&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Promoting NetSuite adoption across the organization&nbsp;</span></li></ul><h1 style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-size:18pt;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:24px;margin-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;\"><b><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Experience</strong></b></h1><ul data-pattern=\"discCircleSquare\" data-depth=\"1\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;margin:8px 0px;line-height:1.6;padding:0px 0px 0px 32px;list-style-type:disc;\"><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">At least 3 years of relevant experience in an international SaaS or technology company&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Proficiency</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">in Excel and all other Microsoft Office applications&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:11pt;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Demonstrated success in fast-paced work environments&nbsp;</span></li></ul><h1 style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-size:18pt;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:24px;margin-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;\"><b><strong style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Desirable </strong></b></h1><ul data-pattern=\"discCircleSquare\" data-depth=\"1\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Basel Grotesk&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;margin:8px 0px;line-height:1.6;padding:0px 0px 0px 32px;list-style-type:disc;\"><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:10pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">Experience in delivering In-depth financial modelling and scenario analysis</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:10pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">Experience with collaborating with investment bankers and senior stakeholders</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:10pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">Experience in supporting due diligence processes</span></li><li style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);font-size:10pt;margin:3px 0px;letter-spacing:0.25px;line-height:1.6;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(111,111,114);white-space:pre-wrap;\">Experience with NetSuite</span></li></ul>"
